title: #140 - Mick West
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast we are joined by scientific skeptic Mick West! Together we discuss flat earth theories, jet fuel melting steel beams, what really happened to Jeffery Epstein, Bob Lazar and Area 51, and a whole lot more!
